node.text:
🍥 NEW PRODUCT 🍥
Super excited to reveal the second new fur bag coming next Friday (13th)!
Pre-orders will be for a limited time and there will be a discount if you order both bags as well as a free pre order gift for the first 200 orders!
They are just PERFECT for trips out when you don't want to lug too much around with you - and looks super cute too!
The faux fur is so soft and we have even added a cute egg zipper detail.
Sign up to our newsletter and/or turn notifications on to not miss out 💕
.
.
.

node.text:
Meet Watermeli! She is this month's limited edition pin club and trading card!
Alongside watermelon kitty, Pi who forgot where his mouth was, Kumo trying to eat a slice twice her size and miso & Chu set sail the watermelon boat 🍉
Also some adorable summer vibes watermelon washi tape!
.
Sign up at: 
www.stamistudios.com/pinclub (signs ups close 24th August)
.
Pins are posted out after the 24th of each month.
.
Pin club members also get continuous store discount (up to 20%), free wallpapers, sneak peeks, discord perks, free monthly star pins, extra Stami stars to spend & access to the secret shop with exclusives as well as first chances!
.
.
.
